"WITH sub AS (SELECT aas.app_id, " + "       count(aas.account_id)                                                      AS allCount, " + "       count(CASE WHEN ((aas.subscription -> 'fullSum')::decimal > 0) THEN 1 END) AS paidCount " + "             FROM account_app_subscription aas " + "                      JOIN account_app aa " + "                                ON aas.app_id = aa.app_id AND aa.account_id = aas.account_id " + "                                    AND aa.install_time >= " + "(now() - (#{interval}::text || ' days')::interval) " + "             WHERE (aas.ticket -> 'source' -> 'automatic')::bool is false " + "             GROUP BY aas.app_id) " + "SELECT ac.app_id      AS appId, " + "       ac.category_id AS categoryId, " + "       ac.sorting, " + "       app.title      AS appTitle, " + "       app.alias      AS appAlias, " + "       app.status     AS appStatus, " + "       cat.title      AS categoryTitle, " + "       v.title        AS vendorTitle " + "FROM application_category ac " + "         JOIN application app ON app.id = ac.app_id " + "         JOIN vendor v ON app.vendor_id = v.id " + "         JOIN category cat ON cat.id = ac.category_id AND cat.id = #{categoryId} " + "         LEFT JOIN sub ON ac.app_id = sub.app_id " + "ORDER BY v.alias = 'moysklad' DESC, " + "         COALESCE(sub.paidCount, 0) DESC, " + "         COALESCE(sub.allCount, 0) DESC, " + "         app.title;"
